    <title>Welcome to My Website!</title>
    <url>/index.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p>I am a Ph.D. in fundamental mathematics graduated from AMSS, UCAS<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn1" id="fnref1">[1]</a></sup> in 2020. 😀</p>
<p>The website source code can be found <span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL2xpcGNhdHkvbGlwY2F0eS5naXRodWIuaW8=">here<i class="fa fa-external-link-alt"></i></span>.</p>
<p><img data-src="index/daiyuzanghua.jpg" alt></p>
<div style="text-align:center;"><font size="2">黛玉葬花, painted by 费丹旭(English: Fei Danxu), 1801–1850(Qing Dynasty)</font></div>
<hr class="footnotes-sep">
<section class="footnotes">
<ol class="footnotes-list">
<li id="fn1" class="footnote-item"><p><font size="3"> In this website,  “AMSS,UCAS” = Academy of Mathematics and Systems Science, University of Chinese Academy of Sciences</font> <a href="#fnref1" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p>
</li>
</ol>
</section>
